                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <h6>Platform Support:</h6>
                    <ul class="small">
                        <li><strong>Windows:</strong> Windows Hello, FIDO2 security keys</li>
                        <li><strong>macOS:</strong> Touch ID, FIDO2 security keys</li>
